### Government Tender Announcement

#### Food Catering Services SW Ontario

This is a request for proposal for the provision of food catering services for the Department of National Defence, located in the southwestern region of Ontario.

**Reference Number:** PW-_KIN-950-8697
**Amendment Number:** 1
**Solicitation Number:** W3027-211123/C
**Publication Date:** 2022-10-05
**Tender Closing Date:** 2022-10-24

**Tender Status:** Expired
**GSIN:** K102B - Food Catering Services
**UNSPSC:** None
**Procurement Category:** SRV - Service

**Description:**

The Department of National Defence (DND), 31 Canadian Brigade Group (31 CBG), and Regional Cadet Support Unit (RCSU) require food catering services throughout Region 1 - Windsor, Region 2 - Cedar Springs, Chatham, and Region 4 - Sarina, on an as-and-when-required basis.

**Trade Agreements:**

- Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
- Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
- Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)
- Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
- Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
- Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
- World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
- Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
- Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
